text: Bus station with covered connection to Phoenix  LRT with plenty of dinning shopping banking library postage supermarkets  community centre cinemas entertainment and amenities nearby. One stop to Hillion Mall and Ten Mile Juction. Connecting to Choa chu Kang NS line via LRT. Buses to Bukit Timah too. Nearest LRT to Singapore Post Bukit Panjang. Named after Phoenix Height private housing estate. Friendly cosy comfy welcoming ambience for romantic intimates groups students tourists expats locals visitors and families.
The easiest and most conveinent for travelling around the vicinity..
A mini roller coaster ride on the LRT
